summary: This is a brief email or memo summarizing a call between a Special Agent (SA) and Dan Besselsen on November 26, 2021. The discussion covered travel logistics and timing, and a request was made for Dan Besselsen to send output from an attendance database for a specific individual (whose name is redacted) to replace an existing exhibit (3528-005). The document is subject to a protective order.
